Design for OptionSmooth

Overview
	This program is for determining which symbols (AAPL) are a good earnings play.
	
Requirements

	must support alternate time frames for determining the options to use
	must show all options ready to trade during earnings.
	
Usage

	optionSmooth.pl [-d date] [-ot typeOfOptionsToGather] 
	
	-d date to use instead of default
	-ot option type. weekly|monthly default is weekly
	
	